    dc:description "PLATE 7. Figures 1–8. Longiantrum, Abes, Asyprocessa, Tantulius, and Asymelissa species, adults. 1, Longiantrum coclea, female holotype, Vietnam N, Ban En Base Camp; 2, L. legraini, female holotype, Thailand, Loei; 3, L. burmaensis, male holotype, Myanmar N, Htawgaw; 4, L. quadra, male holotype, Vietnam N, Tonkin; 5, Abes vedi, female holotype, Thailand N, Chiang Mai; 6, Asyprocessa wapi, male holotype, Laos, Wapi; 7, A. laevi, female holotype, Thailand, Chiang Mai; 8, A. spinus, male holotype, Malaysia W, Penang." ;
